FT  04 MAY 93 / Airlines criticise Heathrow rents
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
INTERNATIONAL airlines operating from Heathrow airport's Terminal 3 have
attacked BAA, which operates London's airports, for charging excessive
rents.
