diagnosis of the illness, which many had suspected for months.
Sir Roy, 67, has not contacted his family or Thames Water since his driver
left him at his Battersea flat at 2pm on Tuesday.
Police divers were reported to have searched the River Thames near his flat
yesterday but found no trace.
